title: #92Noon! Zim/Falvey/Leber/Florio/Ripken/Musberger
description: Jam packed Thursday! Atopics to start, then a replay of X's & O's chat PA had with Mike Zimmer, and Twins CBO Derek Falvey finishes out the first hour. Ben Leber is in studio, Vikings/Raiders 1-on-1s, and the final hour goes Football with Florio, MLB Network's Bill Ripken and Uncle Brent Musberger finishes out the show!
